Folks,

We have requested 2 meeting slots for Prague: a 2 hour and a 1 hour. We may=
 not get the full 2 meetings, as this depends on whether we can show we act=
ually need them. Time in Dallas at the last IETF was very tight. In order t=
o better gauge how much time we will need, we'd like to get an initial idea=
 about the agenda.

Please let us know if you would like a slot in Prague. As always, we can't =
guarantee we will grant all requests, but knowing them ahead of time is alw=
ays better.

Thanks,

chairs

--_000_BN1PR03MB0727350D329F1F941F5BC6D95BE0BN1PR03MB072namprd_
