Hi Alex,

Do you have any news on any Bluetooth SIG plans to create some version of
BLE that can be compatible with classic Bluetooth?

Since the Bluetooth protocol stack has been significantly redesigned for
Bluetooth Low Energy, these are actually two different technologies,
similar to considering IEEE 802.15.4 and IEEE 802.11. We don't expect them
to interoperate.

Best regards,

Carles



