 this rule, it will use an ISM band below 1Ghz. The exact frequency depends=
 on the region. In a reference document from IEEE (https://mentor.ieee.org/=
802.11/dcn/11/11-11-1296-03-00ah-potential-channelization-for-11ah.pptx) yo=
