Does that stack correspond to a packet like this(?):

  +--------------------+------------+-------------+------------+-------+
  | 802.11 Data Header | LLC Header | 6lowpan IPHC|IPv6 Header |Payload|
  +--------------------+------------+-------------+------------+-------+

