because they'd negate the advantage of comressing headers in the first 
place.

Is it possible to carry 6lowpan headers without wrapping them? (like 
EthernetII carries IPv6 Base Headers).

>         6LoWPAN uses the first byte of the MAC payload (the "dispatch"
