Further comments inline, bracketed by <RCC2></RCC2>. The part you are
missing is that these extra headers are never on the wire/ether. They are
added by the network adapter ("dongle") simply for Wireshark's (and other
network analysers) convenience. So there is no consequence for packet sizes
on the wire/ether.

Robert


