> should all become clear.

Yes, I am taking all necessary time to analyze packets.

In return, would you take the time to tell what _would_ you think of 
this header stack if 6lowpan header were optional?

(no EthernetII)
802.15.4 Data
LLC Header
IPv6 Base Header
payload

Alex


